<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="life-n">life <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /laɪf/    美 /laɪf/  </p>
<p>(pl lives)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 生存；生命：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The right to life is the most basic of human rights.
生存权是最基本的人权。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thousands <strong>lost their lives</strong> in the earthquake. 
成千上万的人在地震中丧生。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 生物；活物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Plants are necessary for life on the Earth. 
对地球上的生物来说，植物是必不可少的。</p><footer>2012 四川</footer></div>

<h4 id="3-c-u">3.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 一生；终身：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has never been to London <strong>in his life</strong>.
他一生从未到过伦敦。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A good friend is a friend <strong>for life</strong>.
好朋友是终生的朋友。</p></div>

<h4 id="4-c-u">4.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 生活；人生：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>city / school / working life
城市/学校/工作生活</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>lead</strong> / <strong>live</strong> / <strong>have</strong> <strong>a</strong> ... <strong>life</strong>
过…的生活</p></div>

<h4 id="5-u">5.★ <strong>[U] 活力；生气；活跃</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She looks like any other schoolgirl, fresh-faced and full of life.
她看起来和其他女生一样，有张稚嫩的脸并充满活力。</p><footer>2017 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="all-ones-life">all one's life</h3>
<p>1.<strong>终生；一辈子：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bell was an inventor all his life.  
贝尔终生都在搞发明。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 3</footer></div>

<h3 id="bring-to-life">bring … to life</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使苏醒过来；使更生动：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He asks the Greek Goddess to bring her to life.
他请求希腊女神让她复活。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 4</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The new teacher always brought the class to life with his humor. 
新来的老师总是用他的幽默把课上得生动活泼。</p></div>

<h3 id="come-to-life">come to life</h3>
<p>1.<strong>苏醒过来；变得活跃 (come alive)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When the girl finally came to life, we began to breathe easily. 
当女孩最终醒过来时我们才松了一口气。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The match came to life in the final minutes of the second half.
比赛在下半场的最后几分钟变得精彩起来。</p></div>

<h3 id="life-and-or-death">life and / or death</h3>
<p>1.<strong>生死攸关的；关系重大的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a life and death decision
生死攸关的决定</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>You can change your job, you can move house, but friendship is meant to be <strong><em>_</em></strong> life.  （2012 安徽改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>